# Mastercard Cybersecurity Simulation – Forage

This project simulates the role of a Security Awareness Analyst at Mastercard as part of a virtual experience program on [Forage](https://www.theforage.com/). The focus was on identifying phishing threats and designing educational resources to strengthen internal cybersecurity awareness.

## 🧪 Project Objectives

- Analyze real-world phishing techniques and indicators
- Craft a simulated phishing email to test employee awareness
- Create a security awareness presentation to educate users on phishing prevention

## 🗂️ Included Files

- `crafted-phishing-email.pdf` – A simulated phishing email created to raise awareness of common social engineering tactics
- `phishing-sim-presentation.pdf` – A presentation designed to educate internal employees on identifying phishing attempts and improving their cybersecurity posture

## 🔧 Tools & Skills Used

- Technical writing and visual communication
- Threat analysis (phishing identification)
- End-user security training development
- Security awareness campaign strategy

## 🎯 Outcome

Through this simulation, I strengthened my understanding of phishing techniques, developed communication materials to support security culture, and gained insight into the responsibilities of a cybersecurity awareness professional.

## 📅 Completion Date

June 2025

